value: Crime Master Gogo naam hai mera! Ankhen nikal ke gotiyaan kheltaan hoon.
Aayan hoon, kuch to le ke jaoonga!
Teja! yeh kaise aadmi tune paal rakhe hain, saale suit to 10–10 hazaar ka pehente hain, lekin akal 10 paise ki bhi nahi hai
Plan! Plan! Saala Plan! Tejaaa! Yeh kaise admi tune paal rakhe hain, saale baatein to sher cheeteh ki karte hain magar khud ki aukaat choohe jitni bhi nahin
Khandani chor hoon, Mogambo ka bhateeja
Yeh Teja Teja kya hai… yeh Teja Teja
